entropy

Normality

  • Midlife Males : p = 0.0086614

  • Midlife females : p = 0.105213

  • Young males : p = 0.0807839

  • Young females : p = 0.2216843



ANOVA and Effect Sizes

Running a two factor anova with interactions. Main effect of age but not sex

entropy_aov <- aov(formula=entropy ~ sex * agegroup, masterDF)
summary(entropy_aov)
